Autumn brings on a more muted tone when it comes to make-up by replacing bright bold ... hues, as I find these most flattering to my skin tone and hair. The formulas non-drying and very easy to apply. This is one of Huda Beauty’s favourite shades from her collection and I can totally see why! It doesn’t wash out my pale skin and really ... non-drying, very lightweight and comfortable on the lips. The price point isn’t to high and I’m still torn between the Huda Beauty & Jouer Cosmetics matte lipsticks and both work really well and have a variety of pretty colours.
